This product includes software developed as the open developer surface of the
Atlas autonomous-lab framework: the Atlas Protocol (ALP) contract library
(`atlas-protocol`, in protocol/) and the `atlas` developer CLI (`atlas-sdk`,
in sdk/).

This repository contains ONLY that open surface. The Atlas engine — including
the verification-firewall implementation, the per-lab compounding ledger, and
physical-instrument bridges — is a separate work and is not licensed under
this repository.

